spec_data.Name: nodejs-object-dot-omit
spec_data.Description:
Return a copy of an object excluding the given key, or array of keys. Also
accepts an optional filter function as the last argument.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:37:08 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Return a copy of an object excluding the given key
